## Data Flow Rules

### Database Schema (Drizzle)
```typescript
// frontend/src/db/schema.ts
// Primary tables:
// - mps (460 MPs)
// - senators (100 Senators)
// - bills (Legislative projects)
// - votings (Sittings and individual votes)
// - sync_logs (Synchronization history)
```

### Data Fetching Pattern (Drizzle)
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT: Use Drizzle queries in Server Components
// lib/db/queries.ts
import { db } from "@/db";
import { bills } from "@/db/schema";

export async function getBills() {
  return await db.select().from(bills);
}

// app/ustawy/page.tsx
export default async function BillsPage() {
  const billsData = await getBills(); 
  return <BillsList bills={billsData} />;
}
```

### Backend Synchronization
```bash
# ✅ CORRECT: Execution of Python sync scripts
cd backend
python3 sync.py      # Synchronizes all sources with PostgreSQL

# ❌ WRONG: Manual table modification without using sync script
# (risks data inconsistency)
```

---

