## Performance Rules

### Server Component Optimization
```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT: Fetch data once in Server Component
export default async function Page() {
  const data = await getData();  // Runs on server, cached
  return <ClientComponent data={data} />;
}

// ❌ WRONG: Fetching in Client Component
"use client";
export default function Page() {
  const [data, setData] = useState([]);
  useEffect(() => { fetch(/* ... */) }, []);  // Extra roundtrip
}
```

### Image Optimization
```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT: Use Next.js Image for photos
import Image from 'next/image';
<Image src={mp.photoUrl} alt={mp.name} width={48} height={48} />

// ❌ WRONG: Plain <img> tag
<img src={mp.photoUrl} />  {/* No optimization */}
```

